	 <title>System.ToString</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para><symbol>Boolian, Byte, Date, DateTime, Decimal, Guid, Integer, Long,
		  Money, Short, Time, TimeSpan,</symbol> and <symbol>VersionNumber</symbol> types
		  can be explicitly converted to <symbol>String</symbol> using this
		  operator.</para> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>select ToString(123.45*83); // Long
select ToString(DateTime() + ToTimeSpan("714hours")); // DateTime
select ToString("yes" = "Yes"); // boolean</programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>10246.35
2004-05-26 19:53:49
false</programlisting> 
	 </example> 
